79
00:04:35,190 --> 00:04:36,630
Fire!

80
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:38,460
It's a bath.

81
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:39,250
That's it?

82
00:04:39,460 --> 00:04:42,190
Don't go scarin' people, Sensei.

83
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:43,960
But if it's a bath, relax.

84
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:45,560
I can do that.

85
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,470
You know how to do this?

86
00:04:47,470 --> 00:04:47,970
Yep!

87
00:04:48,570 --> 00:04:50,260
Whenever Grampa takes a bath,

88
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:51,850
Enjoying your bath, sir?

89
00:04:50,260 --> 00:04:51,850
I always tend the fire.

90
00:04:50,390 --> 00:04:51,850
Yep!
But put it out
if it gets too big.

91
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:54,800
Are you sure you'll be all right?

92
00:04:55,150 --> 00:04:57,350
Leave it to me! I'm used to it!

93
00:04:58,830 --> 00:05:00,620
Getting it ready was tough,

94
00:05:00,620 --> 00:05:03,390
but it's kind of exciting,
like I'm visiting a hot spring.

95
00:05:05,130 --> 00:05:05,970
Hot!

96
00:05:06,830 --> 00:05:08,350
Sensei, is it too hot?!

97
00:05:08,350 --> 00:05:10,200
No, it's fine.

98
00:05:11,730 --> 00:05:13,370
Thank goodness...

99
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:16,120
Ahh, I've come back to life...

100
00:05:17,470 --> 00:05:19,410
It's permeating right to the bone.

101
00:05:19,410 --> 00:05:22,030
I can see why the village chief is into this.

102
00:05:22,030 --> 00:05:23,960
It's like a reward for the effort.

103
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,340
Sensei, there's trouble!

104
00:05:26,340 --> 00:05:27,090
What's wrong?!

105
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,260
Oops!

106
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:32,660
Naru!

107
00:05:32,660 --> 00:05:34,960
Why are they here?!

108
00:05:35,910 --> 00:05:37,480
They thought there was a fire.

109
00:05:37,610 --> 00:05:40,470
A kid tendin' the fire while you have a nice bath?

110
00:05:40,470 --> 00:05:42,120
As punishment, we'll see you naked!

111
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,190
I don't get your reasoning!

112
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:46,360
Weren't ya really wantin' young girls to see ya?

113
00:05:46,650 --> 00:05:49,010
Don't talk like I'm an exhibitionist!

114
00:05:49,010 --> 00:05:50,370
There's no fire here, so leave!

115
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:53,990
As always, he can't take a joke.

116
00:05:55,790 --> 00:05:57,170
What's that camera for?

117
00:05:57,170 --> 00:05:59,760
I thought I'd collect reference
material for my manga.

118
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:01,110
Reference material...

119
00:06:01,110 --> 00:06:03,590
But ya can't show full nudity,
even in manga, right?

120
00:06:03,590 --> 00:06:06,420
It'll be fine, if I add a mosaic over the tip.

121
00:06:06,850 --> 00:06:08,470
So long as you can get the idea...

122
00:06:07,170 --> 00:06:08,950
I can't relax.

123
00:06:08,470 --> 00:06:11,600
No, it's still no good.

124
00:06:09,450 --> 00:06:11,590
Looks like I can't take a bath during the day.

125
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,340
Eh? Why not?

126
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,340
At any rate, for now,

127
00:06:13,340 --> 00:06:16,770
I'll wait until they get bored and leave.

128
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:19,000
It's too hot, idiots!

129
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,300
Run away!

130
00:06:21,170 --> 00:06:22,690
Sensei, is it too hot?

131
00:06:22,820 --> 00:06:24,030
Obviously!

132
00:06:24,030 --> 00:06:25,070
See how red I am?

133
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,000
Run away!

134
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,030
No, don't you run away, too!

135
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:35,020
At any rate, that turned my mood around.

136
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:36,630
Okay, time to wri—

137
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:37,750
Hey.

138
00:06:38,090 --> 00:06:38,650
Hiro!

139
00:06:38,650 --> 00:06:40,690
Wh-What are you doing here?!

140
00:06:40,690 --> 00:06:42,400
Mom's out today,

141
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:44,000
