Actually, this is awful, too.

170
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,330
Wait a minute!

171
00:07:38,330 --> 00:07:40,140
You just said it was great!

172
00:07:40,140 --> 00:07:42,030
I never said it was great.

173
00:07:42,030 --> 00:07:43,350
All I can taste is miso.

174
00:07:43,350 --> 00:07:45,860
Why're you so stubborn? That's immature.

175
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:47,760
Who are you calling immature?!

176
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:48,680
I'm older than you!

177
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,910
It's impolite to point!

178
00:07:49,910 --> 00:07:52,680
If you're older, act your age and admit defeat!

179
00:07:56,590 --> 00:07:58,110
Sensei!

180
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:01,360
What's wrong, Hina?!

181
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,830
Did something happen?

182
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:06,240
