Here, Hina. Drink this and calm down.

185
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:14,550
If she came over in such a rush, then it
must be an emergency! Tell us, quickly!

186
00:08:14,930 --> 00:08:17,530
We don't need to rush so much
for a child's emergency.

187
00:08:17,530 --> 00:08:18,940
But aren't you curious?!

188
00:08:18,940 --> 00:08:21,760
You're being immature again.

189
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:25,210
All right, Hina! Just calm down!

190
00:08:25,210 --> 00:08:26,540
We'll listen to you!

191
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,190
Naru...

192
00:08:28,190 --> 00:08:33,240
Naru's getting picked on by grade
schoolers from the next village!

193
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,240
This way!

194
00:08:38,930 --> 00:08:40,160
Naru! You all right?!

195
00:08:41,430 --> 00:08:45,240
Cut it out!

196
00:08:45,950 --> 00:08:49,230
Actually, that looks like a lot of fun.

197
00:08:49,230 --> 00:08:50,500
Naru!

198
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:52,760
Hina! Save me!

199
00:08:53,140 --> 00:08:54,640
You went and got grown-ups?!

200
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:55,380
Coward!

201
00:08:55,820 --> 00:08:57,630
Where are you kids from?

202
00:08:57,630 --> 00:08:59,900
This is their playground.

203
00:08:59,900 --> 00:09:01,800
Shut up, fox-faced jerk!

204
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,600
We just took over this place!

205
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:05,380
Fox-faced jerk...

206
00:09:05,380 --> 00:09:07,760
They're from Rokunosaki Village.

207
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:10,690
