neighboring village for ages.

208
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:13,550
Sensei, make 'em go away!

209
00:09:13,550 --> 00:09:15,700
We were playin' here first!

210
00:09:16,020 --> 00:09:17,220
Uh, sure.

211
00:09:17,790 --> 00:09:18,610
Hey!

212
00:09:18,610 --> 00:09:19,700
Kids from the next village!

213
00:09:20,590 --> 00:09:23,260
How dare you call someone you've
just met a "fox-faced jerk"?

214
00:09:23,810 --> 00:09:24,700
How am I a fox?

215
00:09:24,700 --> 00:09:26,950
Sure, sometimes people say
I have a mean look in my eyes,

216
00:09:26,950 --> 00:09:28,170
but only sometimes!

217
00:09:28,460 --> 00:09:31,300
